# The Wizard King's Decree — environment template.
#
# Copy to `.env` and `source` it (or export these) before a LIVE run. The
# offline test-suite needs NONE of these. Secrets are read from the environment
# ONLY and are never written to any config file or the SQLite store.

# --- API keys (SPEC §17.1) ---
# The Council of Mages:
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...        # Claude Opus 4.8 (mage A + King styling)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...               # GPT (mage B)
# The independent Court Historian (MUST be a proper Gemini API key, independent
# of the archbox OpenCode/Google OAuth flow — see Archbox Known Issue #4):
GEMINI_API_KEY=...

# --- Harvest sources (optional; unset = harvesting is a no-op) ---
# Comma-separated RSS/Atom feed URLs for datable upcoming events:
# WKD_NEWS_FEEDS=https://example.com/calendar.rss,https://example.org/feed.xml
# A prediction-market / forecasting questions JSON endpoint (harvested for the
# QUESTIONS only — never traded, SPEC §2):
# WKD_MARKET_ENDPOINT=https://example.com/api/questions

# --- Structural overrides (optional; win over the --config file) ---
# WKD_DB_PATH=wkd.db
# WKD_CHRONICLE_DIR=chronicle
# WKD_CHRONICLE_PORT=8787
# WKD_DAILY_DECREE_CAP=6
# WKD_DELIBERATION_MAX_ROUNDS=3
# WKD_CHECKPOINT_INTERVAL_DAYS=7
# Free-pick leg (SPEC §7): how many matters of his own choosing the King may
# originate per run from live headlines (0 disables; default 3):
# WKD_FREE_PICK_MAX=3
